# Aider AI Rules - Kancelaria Adwokacka Website

## Project Overview
Law office website: Bootstrap 5 + HTML + CSS + JavaScript (NO TypeScript/React)

## Stack
- Frontend: HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript ES6+
- Framework: Bootstrap 5.3.2
- Build: Vite 5.0
- Icons: Font Awesome 6.5.1

## Key Requirements
1. **RODO Compliance**: Forms need data processing consent
2. **Accessibility**: WCAG 2.1 AA (screen readers, keyboard navigation)
3. **Responsive**: Mobile-first design
4. **SEO**: Local legal services (Trzebnica region)
5. **Polish**: Professional language for legal context

## Coding Standards
- HTML: Semantic elements, proper headings, alt text
- CSS: Mobile-first, BEM naming, Bootstrap utilities
- JS: ES6+ (const/let, arrow functions, async/await)

## Form Template (RODO)
```html
<form>
  <input type="email" required aria-label="Email">
  <textarea required aria-label="Wiadomość"></textarea>
  <input type="checkbox" required>
  <label>Zgoda RODO na przetwarzanie danych</label>
  <button type="submit">Wyślij</button>
</form>
```

## Development
```bash
npm run dev      # Dev server
npm run lint     # Check code
npm run format   # Auto-format
npm test         # Run tests
```

